@prefix ex: <https://vocab.cfaa.eus/broaching/> .
ex:InterfazUsuario_3 a ex:InterfazUsuario ;
    ex:textoExtracto "Operations at the interface. Minimize/Maximize the CNC. Show / hide the virtual operator panel. Show / hide the PLC message list. Show / hide the CNC message list. Show / hide the window for errors and warnings. Turn the CNC off. Work modes. To show the task window. MAIN MENU Main menu. AUTO Automatic mode. MANUAL Jog mode. EDIT EDISIMU mode. MDI MDI/MDA mode. [ CTRL] + [F10] TABLES User tables. [ CTRL] + [F11] TOOLS Tool and magazine table. [ CTRL] + [F12] UTILITIES Utilities mode. CALC Calculator. Browsing keys. [ CTRL] + [F1] BACK Previous menu. [ CTRL] + [F2] FOCUS Switch window. [ CTRL] + [F3] NEXT Switch screens. Two-colored key. Execution keys. [ CTRL]+[S] Cycle start key (START). [ CTRL]+[P] Cycle stop key (STOP). [ CTRL]+[R] RESET Reset key. SINGLE Single-block execution mode. The shortcuts for the [START] [STOP] and [RESET] keys are only available when the CNC is installed as simulator on a PC." .

ex:ModoOperacion_AUTOMATIC a ex:ModoOperacion ;
    ex:identificador "AUTO" ;
    ex:textoExtracto "AUTO Automatic mode." ;
    ex:textoExtracto "The shortcuts for the [START] [STOP] and [RESET] keys are only available when the CNC is installed as simulator on a PC." .

